headline: GTA Online
subtitle: A BUMPY RIDE
content:
Grab your Junk and buckle your helmet, because fresh and exercise are about to get an upgrade. That’s right, if you’re brave enough to hit the trails face-first then saddle up, beat the time, smash the record, and plummet straight into a rock-solid crashmat of GTA$ and RP.

Junk Energy Time Trials are now available daily. Literal crashmats are not.
